snippet.title: BULLET SOUL for Windows PC (Steam®) Trailer
snippet.description:
A brand-new adaptation to the shooting genre which rewards survival through aggressive play. Blending classic shooting game design with a substantial dose of modern day bullet hell, Bullet Soul has it all!

[Steam Store]
http://store.steampowered.com/app/544580/
